channel.title: ExtremeX RSPS 718/742
channel.description:
Welcome to the brand new server: ExtremeX!
We are a brand new rsps, starting fresh with stuff you've never seen before! We have customs, fully working Kiln and Jad, everything you could think of for a great server like this one! Website: extremexrsps.webs.com/ Forums are also located here! Download: On the website! And if me telling you wasn't enough, I have screenshots!: Home: tinypic.com/view.php?pic=15n0nzs&s=5
Teleports: tinypic.com/view.php?pic=335ehci&s=5
Fully working Clan Wars: tinypic.com/view.php?pic=2njiqes&s=5
Kiln: tinypic.com/view.php?pic=2ivh72v&s=5
I hope to see you on this amazing server!
